<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">

    <div class="account-wall" style="background:none; border:none; margin-top: 6%">
    <h3 style="font-weight:bold;">Welcome!</h3><h4 style="font-weight:bold;"> This assessment is your chance to qualify for the BIG THING!</h4>
  <br>
  <h4>
    Instructions:
  </h4>
  <ul style="padding-left: 16px;">
    <li>This assessment carries 100 marks</li>
    <li>This assessment is divided into 3 sections â€“ Single Response Questions, Multiple Response Questions and Simulation. All the sections have to be completed in order to qualify for the next stage.</li>
    <li>You have only 1 attempt per section. Do not LOG OUT or REFRESH until you have completed all the sections. In case you do, that particular section would be marked as complete and you will be directed to the next section.</li>
    <li>You have 90 minutes to complete this assessment. If you fail to complete the assessment within the stipulated time, your scores will automatically get submitted once the time is over.</li>
    <li>In case you need any assistance, please get in touch with the administrator</li>
  </ul>
  <br>
  <h4>
    Best of Luck!
  </h4>
</div>



  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <!--<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4 col-xs-offset-4 col-sm-offset-4 col-md-offset-4 col-lg-offset-4">-->

    <div class="account-wall">
      <h3 class="form_heading">Create an account</h3>
      <!--<hr class="line_style">-->
      <img src="/assets/line.png" class="line_style">

      <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name), :html => {:class => "form-signin"}) do |f| %>
          <%= devise_error_messages! %>
          <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, :placeholder => "Email", :class => "form-control", :required=>true %>

          <%= f.text_field :name, :placeholder => "Name", :class => "form-control", :required=>true, :style=>"margin-top: 6px;" %>

          <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", :placeholder => "Password", :class => "form-control", :required=>true %>
          <% if @validatable %>
              <em>(<%= @minimum_password_length %> characters minimum)</em>
          <% end %><br />

          <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off", :placeholder => "Password Confirmation", :class => "form-control", :required=>true %>

          <%= f.submit "Sign up", :class => "btn btn-lg  btn-block button_style" %>

      <% end %>

      <div style="text-align: center">
        <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
      </div>

    </div>

    <hr>
    <p class="text-center">Site best viewed in Mozilla Firefox and Google Chrome.</p>

  </div>
</div>
